              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">❌ Cons:</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>• No AI features</li>
                  <li>• Limited search functionality</li>
                  <li>• No OCR recipe scanning</li>
                  <li>• Outdated interface</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Paprika is a solid traditional recipe manager with reliable import features and one-time pricing, but lacks modern AI-powered capabilities.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- AllRecipes -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-6 border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">3. AllRecipes Dinner Spinner</h3>
                <div class="text-yellow-400 text-lg mb-2">★★★☆☆ 3.8/5</div>
                <p class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">🌟 Best for Recipe Discovery</p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Free</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Ad-supported</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">✅ Pros:</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>• Huge recipe database</li>
                  <li>• Community reviews</li>
                  <li>• Free to use</li>
                  <li>• Recipe recommendations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">❌ Cons:</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>• Heavy ads</li>
                  <li>• Limited organization</li>
                  <li>• No meal planning</li>
                  <li>• Poor import features</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              AllRecipes is great for discovering new recipes but lacks the organization and planning features needed for serious home cooks.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why TasteBuddy is the Best Recipe App -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Why TasteBuddy is the Best Recipe App in 2025</h2>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🤖</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">AI-Powered Intelligence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                TasteBuddy is the only recipe app that uses AI to generate personalized meal plans, transform recipes for dietary needs, and create beautiful recipe images. This makes meal planning effortless and cooking more enjoyable.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📸</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">OCR Recipe Scanning</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Unlike competitors, TasteBuddy can scan recipes from cookbooks and magazines using OCR technology. Simply take a photo and the app converts it to a digital recipe automatically.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🥗</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Dietary Transformations</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Transform any recipe to fit your dietary needs with intelligent ingredient substitutions. Convert recipes to vegan, gluten-free, low-carb, or any other preference instantly.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛒</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Smart Shopping Lists</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Automatically generate shopping lists from your meal plans with ingredients organized by store aisles. The app even combines duplicate ingredients across multiple recipes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How to Choose the Best Recipe App -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">How to Choose the Best Recipe App for You</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">🎯 Consider Your Cooking Goals</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Are you looking to organize existing recipes, discover new ones, or plan entire meals? Apps like TasteBuddy excel at comprehensive meal planning, while AllRecipes is better for recipe discovery.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">💰 Budget Considerations</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Free apps like AllRecipes have ads and limited features. One-time purchases like Paprika ($5-$20) offer good value but lack AI features. Subscription apps like TasteBuddy ($4.99/month) provide the most advanced features.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">📱 Device Compatibility</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                Make sure your chosen app works across all your devices. TasteBuddy and Paprika offer excellent cross-platform sync, while some apps are limited to specific platforms.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/90 to-[#1C2513]/80 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2A2D24]/30">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">🍽️ Dietary Needs</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                If you have specific dietary requirements, choose an app that can filter and transform recipes accordingly. TasteBuddy's AI dietary transformation feature is unmatched in this area.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/80 to-[#1C2513]/70 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#2A2D24]/30 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">What is the best free recipe app?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">AllRecipes Dinner Spinner is the best free recipe app for discovering new recipes, but it has ads and limited organization features. For advanced features like meal planning and AI assistance, TasteBuddy offers a free version with premium upgrades.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/80 to-[#1C2513]/70 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#2A2D24]/30 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Can recipe apps import from any website?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">TasteBuddy and Paprika can import recipes from most websites automatically. TasteBuddy works with 95% of recipe sites and also includes OCR scanning for cookbook recipes that other apps can't handle.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/80 to-[#1C2513]/70 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#2A2D24]/30 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Which recipe app has the best meal planning features?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">TasteBuddy has the most advanced meal planning features with AI-generated weekly meal plans, automatic shopping list generation, and dietary preference integration. It goes far beyond basic calendar-based meal planning.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1C2513]/80 to-[#1C2513]/70 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#2A2D24]/30 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Do recipe apps work offline?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Most recipe apps including TasteBuddy and Paprika store recipes locally for offline access. However, features like recipe import and AI meal planning require an internet connection.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00CE31]/40 to-[#00CE31]/30 rounded-3xl p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm border border-[#00CE31]/30">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Try the Best Recipe App?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Join thousands of home cooks who have discovered the power of AI-assisted meal planning and recipe organization.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
            <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6554007741"
               class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4"
               target="_blank" 
               rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Download TasteBuddy Free
            </a>
            <a href="/comparisons/tastebuddy-vs-paprika/" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4">
              Compare with Paprika
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </Main>
</Layout>